        <abstract>
            <p>Has verified J. M. Bechstein’s contention that species of finches hybridise.</p>
            <p>Quotes Thomas Bewick’s observations on hybrids between pheasants and common fowl. RGM had often noticed so-called "pheasant fowl", but thought it was a foreign bird.</p>
